00:15:18.627 --> 00:15:19.726
It was true.

218
00:15:20.866 --> 00:15:22.866
Yoo Bum really drove the car.

219
00:15:28.806 --> 00:15:29.806
Yoo Bum!

220
00:15:30.237 --> 00:15:31.337
Ms. Nam!

221
00:15:32.607 --> 00:15:33.746
Stop!

222
00:15:37.346 --> 00:15:38.647
Jae Chan, what's going on?

223
00:15:39.217 --> 00:15:40.947
Hey, call the police right now.

224
00:15:41.016 --> 00:15:43.317
Tell them to stop the car with the plate number ending in 4773.

225
00:15:44.556 --> 00:15:46.886
Have you lost your mind? Call the police and say what?

226
00:15:46.886 --> 00:15:49.926
"According to my brother's dream, there will be an accident soon"?

227
00:15:50.297 --> 00:15:51.627
This is crazy.

228
00:15:51.797 --> 00:15:53.397
You're acting so weird.

229
00:15:53.467 --> 00:15:55.096
Why do you care so much about that girl?

230
00:15:55.096 --> 00:15:56.636
It's not that I care about her. I just...

231
00:15:59.937 --> 00:16:01.706
I just don't want her to end up like me.

232
00:16:02.536 --> 00:16:04.676
What if she lets him dump everything on her like an idiot?

233
00:16:05.306 --> 00:16:08.007
Meeting Yoo Bum again must've really stressed you out.

234
00:16:08.147 --> 00:16:09.846
That's probably why you had that nightmare.

235
00:16:13.116 --> 00:16:14.386
Come on.

236
00:16:15.717 --> 00:16:16.917
Let's go.

237
00:16:20.487 --> 00:16:22.496
Yes, I really should mind my own business.

238
00:16:22.996 --> 00:16:25.127
If I go any further, I'll look like a total lunatic.

239
00:16:37.636 --> 00:16:39.176
Gosh, seriously.

240
00:16:40.306 --> 00:16:42.647
Jae Chan, wait up. Jae Chan, stop!

241
00:16:45.116 --> 00:16:46.846
How can you just take off like that?

242
00:17:02.136 --> 00:17:04.467
An accident? What are you talking about?

243
00:17:04.797 --> 00:17:07.136
Well, I'm not talking about right now.

244
00:17:07.536 --> 00:17:09.437
Something like that might happen in the future.

245
00:17:12.107 --> 00:17:13.976
I'll be okay even if that happens,

246
00:17:14.576 --> 00:17:16.246
so keep my mom safe for me.

247
00:17:16.877 --> 00:17:17.917
Okay.

248
00:17:18.016 --> 00:17:20.717
No matter what happens, I'll be sure...

249
00:17:20.817 --> 00:17:22.817
to keep you and your mom safe. Are we good now?

250
00:17:27.556 --> 00:17:30.027
By the way, what happened between you and Jae Chan?

251
00:17:31.096 --> 00:17:32.627
It looked like he was...

252
00:18:27.886 --> 00:18:29.087
Are you okay?

253
00:19:20.266 --> 00:19:21.366
Did you get hurt?

254
00:19:25.706 --> 00:19:26.906
Are you all right?

255
00:19:28.076 --> 00:19:29.076
Yes.

256
00:19:33.286 --> 00:19:34.286
Jae Chan.

257
00:19:35.047 --> 00:19:36.217
Did you just hit this car?

258
00:19:37.217 --> 00:19:39.687
Yes, I guess my car slipped because of the snow.

259
00:19:40.527 --> 00:19:41.726
This...

260
00:19:42.527 --> 00:19:43.926
was intentional, wasn't it?

261
00:19:44.027 --> 00:19:45.926
No, I told you that my car slipped in the snow.

