308
00:22:31.357 --> 00:22:33.496
and the shock would've killed her mom too.

309
00:22:34.496 --> 00:22:35.697
And that woman...

310
00:22:36.136 --> 00:22:38.837
would've taken her own life like an idiot from feeling victimized.

311
00:22:39.007 --> 00:22:40.136
You...

312
00:22:42.176 --> 00:22:44.337
are more than capable of doing that.

313
00:22:47.976 --> 00:22:49.417
You haven't changed one bit.

314
00:22:49.917 --> 00:22:52.587
You still blame others for everything and give lame excuses.

315
00:22:54.187 --> 00:22:56.187
The truth is, you almost killed us.

316
00:22:58.527 --> 00:22:59.527
No.

317
00:23:00.926 --> 00:23:02.397
I did it to save lives.

318
00:23:16.437 --> 00:23:18.136
Who on earth would believe that?

319
00:23:20.906 --> 00:23:21.917
Hong Joo.

320
00:23:23.277 --> 00:23:24.976
Do you believe what this lunatic is saying?

321
00:23:40.297 --> 00:23:41.326
Right.

322
00:23:42.136 --> 00:23:43.536
Who'd believe me...

323
00:23:44.697 --> 00:23:46.667
if I say that I saw you in my dream...

324
00:23:49.976 --> 00:23:52.147
